---
title: Lemongrass Pork & Rice Bowls with Scallions, Sriracha Mayo & Crispy Fried Onions
description: These irresistible pork and rice bowls are loaded with accouterments that really bring them to life! You’ll sizzle ground pork with Omsom’s legendary Vietnamese-style lemongrass marinade, featuring Red Boat fish sauce for savory complexity, and lots of garlic, lemongrass, and other aromatics. Toss in crisp red cabbage, carrot, and scallion greens for color and balance, then serve it all up with a sprinkle of crispy fried onions and drizzle of spicy-savory Sriracha mayo (just the right finishing touches for the job).
